#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.append.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.append"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:1 of
msgid "Append rows of `other` to the end of caller, returning a new object."
msgstr "将 `other` 的行追加到调用者的末尾，返回一个新对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:3 of
msgid "Columns in `other` that are not in the caller are added as new columns."
msgstr "`other` 中不在调用者中的列将作为新列添加。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:5 of
msgid "The data to append."
msgstr "要追加的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:7 of
msgid "If True, the resulting axis will be labeled 0, 1, …, n - 1."
msgstr "如果为 True，则结果轴将标记为 0, 1, …, n - 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:9 of
msgid "If True, raise ValueError on creating index with duplicates."
msgstr "如果为 True，在创建具有重复值的索引时将引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:11 of
msgid "Sort columns if the columns of `self` and `other` are not aligned."
msgstr "如果 `self` 和 `other` 的列未对齐，则对列进行排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:14 of
msgid "A new DataFrame consisting of the rows of caller and the rows of `other`."
msgstr "一个由调用者和 `other` 的行组成的新 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`concat`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:20 of
msgid "General function to concatenate DataFrame or Series objects."
msgstr "用于连接 DataFrame 或 Series 对象的通用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:23 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:24 of
msgid ""
"If a list of dict/series is passed and the keys are all contained in the "
"DataFrame's index, the order of the columns in the resulting DataFrame "
"will be unchanged."
msgstr ""
"如果传递了 dict/series 列表且键都包含在 DataFrame 的索引中，则结果 "
"DataFrame 中的列顺序将保持不变。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.append.append:28 of
msgid ""
"Iteratively appending rows to a DataFrame can be more computationally "
"intensive than a single concatenate. A better solution is to append those"
" rows to a list and then concatenate the list with the original DataFrame"
" all at once."
msgstr ""
"迭代地向 DataFrame 追加行可能比一次性连接更消耗计算资源。更好的解决方案是"
"将这些行追加到列表中，然后一次性将列表与原始 DataFrame 连接。"

